    {
        "content": "<p>Thanks, looks like that works.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean4\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">simp_rw</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">mul_comm</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
